AI Pipelines
ComfyStream
ComfyStream integration with Livepeer: modular AI inference engine for video frame pipelines on GPU workers.

ComfyStream is a modular AI inference engine that integrates with Livepeer’s Gateway Protocol to execute video frame pipelines on GPU-powered worker nodes. It extends ComfyUI with Livepeer-compatible gateway binding, real-time stream I/O, dynamic node graphs and plugin chaining, and overlay rendering and metadata export.
For a high-level overview and DeepWiki, see the ComfyStream full guide.
